Registration with valid data

1.Open website https://invu.ge
2.Click on “Sign In”
3.Click on "Sign Up Here"
4.Enter valid name  "Sopho"
5.Enter valid surname  "Salamashvili"
6.Enter valid email  "salamashvilisopho@gmail.com"
7.Enter valid password  "Sopo12@"
8.Confirm password "sopo12@"
9.Click “Register” button

Expected Result:
User is successfully registered and redirected to the homepage.




Title: Registration with invalid email data

Steps:
1.Open https://invu.ge
2.Click on “Register”
3.Enter valid name "Sopho"
4.Enter valid surname "Salamashvili"
5.Enter invalid email "sopo.salamashviligmail.com"
6.Enter valid password "sopo123@"
4.Click “Register” button

Expected Result:
The system displays an error: "Please enter a valid email address," and the registration will not be completed.



Title: Registration with a weak password

Steps:
1.Open https://invu.ge
2.Click on “Register”
3.Enter valid name "Sopho"
4.Enter valid surname "Salamashvili"
5.Enter valid email "sopo.salamashvili@gmail.com"
6.Enter a weak password "123456"
4.Click “Register” button

Expected Result:
The system displays an error: "Password is too weak" and registration is not completed.